Output skillguard-scan-ai-sdk.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set Theme { "name": "Whimsy", "black": "#535178", "red": "#ef6487", "green": "#5eca89", "yellow": "#fdd877", "blue": "#65aef7", "magenta": "#aa7ff0", "cyan": "#43c1be", "white": "#ffffff", "background": "#29283b", "foreground": "#b3b0d6" }

Set Width 1200
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 120ms

Type "skillguard scan --path ~/.agents/skills/ai-sdk"
Enter

Sleep 4s